      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed on geometry and operating conditions sufficiently similar to the COU device and operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same platform as the COU device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (3–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Geometric and operational similarity is well-established."
    },
    {
