      "rationale": "SST k-ω selected over realizable k-ε based on superior agreement with FDA benchmark data (mean NIH error 12% vs 19%). Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) used with published constants. Model form uncertainty assessed via turbulence model sensitivity study."
    },
